long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Apply useful keyboard shortcuts to LeetCode.
*Only support Mac OS* currently

- `ctrl + ENTER`: Run Code
- `ctrl + shift + ENTER`: Run Example Testcases
- `command + ENTER`: Submit
- `ctrl/command + t`: Focus testcases
- `ctrl/command + c`: Focus Code Editor
